{"tid":622912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《Call Of Duty》玩家去中東參戰抗 ISIS　從遊戲中學習保命技巧","createTime":"2018-04-09T13:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T14:50:37.000Z","uid":28366,"like":267,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"0726f0335aaccde792ad2dadcccb24a1dc4ef25c","tid":622912,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T13:56:49.000Z","msg":"據外媒報導，指美國一名電玩愛好者 John Duttenhofer ，每天埋首在射擊遊戲《Call of Duty》中。直到去年 4 月，他隻身遠赴敘利亞，加入當地的庫爾德民兵部隊，投身對抗恐怖份子 ISIS 的戰鬥之中。他在訪問中表示，藉著在《Call of Duty》中學到的技巧，他才能在戰場中存活下來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/215544_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F215544_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=99950e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據研究顯示，擅長射擊遊戲的玩家的反應速度較其他人快，而身體肌肉亦更加協調。而 Duttenhofer 亦指，他到戰場後不斷進行體能訓練，更形容射擊遊戲是他的老師。原因在於，他能在遊戲中學到一些基本操作槍械的技巧，更學到在戰鬥中尋找掩護的判斷力。<br />\n<br />\n他亦表示，在戰場最重要的技巧並不是殺敵，而是保命。他於去年辭去工作，更變賣汽車來籌集資金，隻身遠赴敘利亞參戰。 Duttenhofer 表示，雖然家中母親亦無法阻止，但他亦知道參戰這個決定非常自私。更指決定當初參戰，是因為他希望在歷史上留名，而非只會每天埋首工作。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，美軍早已看到射擊遊戲對玩家的吸引力，開發出一款強調真實性的遊戲《American Army》系列遊戲，以吸引玩家入伍參軍。多年來成功吸引不少遊戲內的好手加入美軍，成為荷槍實彈的真正軍人<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/215606_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F215606_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b111728e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/215608_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F215608_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=818b8787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/02/28/cod-player-fight-isis/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2Fcod-player-fight-isis%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=4dxi23YR79Ul%2FUsxr1StjviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f996022f\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/02/28/cod-player-fight-isis/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"9c00a86ff8d798541a810e1db323ee0390d8d37f","tid":622912,"uid":116530,"like":208,"dislike":2,"score":206,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"打機打到真係去參軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4946b5583d7810d1399f5bdc60e53c35e16a53b","tid":622912,"uid":41508,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:03:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9069043a3bde56fb9ce1d4e3994540a53a0ffbec","tid":622912,"uid":95499,"like":118,"dislike":1,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:04:15.000Z","msg":"長遠解決宅男問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2bf7cf37ae0994e43c8969c612407a6e90a308","tid":622912,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dceb7a68edd89f54e93722884240a84062fbb218","tid":622912,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4946b5583d7810d1399f5bdc60e53c35e16a53b","tid":622912,"uid":41508,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:03:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:05:39.000Z","msg":"朱仔成難題:打wargame定打槍game有效啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afc63e566021e31ab5878553fd348fac52532ac","tid":622912,"uid":34461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:06:17.000Z","msg":"respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcb469e1fcb59ef2b19aa9c02195e9adbe4b5ab","tid":622912,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ad